<li>Wine storage (if applicable)</li>
</ul>
<p>Each listing gives Google another signal. A renter searching "10x10 climate controlled storage near me" needs to see that exact unit type on your profile.</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" alt="Google Business Profile optimization for storage facilities" src="/images/blog/storage-facility-gbp-checklist.webp" /></p>
<h3>Post Photos That Sell</h3>
<p>Storage facility photos directly influence rental decisions. Renters want to see clean, well-lit, secure facilities before they visit.</p>
<p>Post 3 to 5 photos per week:</p>
<ul>
