<p>Consistency is everything. Your facility name, address, and phone number must match exactly across every listing. One wrong digit can confuse Google and drop your local pack ranking.</p>
<h3>Local Backlinks</h3>
<p>Target backlinks from organizations in your service area.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Real estate agents and agencies.</strong> Many recommend storage during transitions. Ask to be listed on their resources page.</li>
<li><strong>Moving companies.</strong> Partner with local movers for mutual referrals and website listings.</li>
<li><strong>Apartment complexes.</strong> Offer move-in storage discounts for their residents and get listed on their site.</li>
<li><strong>Local business associations.</strong> Join and get listed on their member directory.</li>
<li><strong>Home staging companies.</strong> Home sellers often need temporary storage. Cross-promote with stagers.</li>
<li><strong>Local news and community sites.</strong> Offer tips for moving season stories.</li>
</ul>
<p>Each local backlink tells Google your storage facility is a trusted part of the community. For a full overview, read our <a href="/blog/local-seo-guide/">local SEO guide</a>.</p>
